# portapop phase-2: record track 1, arm track 2, overdub it (track 1 monitors), play both.
# 100 bpm ~36 f/beat; 4-beat count-in ~144f.
# --- track 1 (armed=0 by default) ---
tap 10 R
tap 160 A
tap 200 S
tap 240 D
tap 280 F
tap 440 R
# --- arm track 2 (index 1): press its ARM button at x=86,y=169 (console) ---
press 460 86 169
release 466 86 169
# --- record track 2, track 1 monitors ---
tap 480 R
tap 630 J
tap 670 K
tap 710 H
tap 900 R
# --- play both (mixdown) ---
tap 920 SPACE
